criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  24 weeks < gestational age < 32 weeks;

          -  500 g ≤ birth weight < 1250 g;

          -  parenteral nutrition with vegetable oil-based lipid emulsions from the first hours of
             life;

          -  diagnosis of cholestasis during vegetable oil-lipid infusion (plasma conjugated
             bilirubin value > 1 mg/dl)

          -  parental consent;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  severe malformations;

          -  inborn errors of metabolism;

          -  severe congenital sepsis;

          -  normal liver functions (plasma conjugated bilirubin under 1 mg/dl during vegetable
             oil-lipid infusion).
